<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV24">
<l>kaṅkainīrpa yantapāta paṅkayattem maṇṇalē</l>
<l>aṅkaiyāḻi caṅkutaṇṭu villumvāḷu mēntiṉāy</l>
<l>ciṅkamāya tēvatēva tēṉulāvu meṉmalar</l>
<l>maṅkaimaṉṉi vāḻumārpa vāḻimēṉi māyaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O our great Lord with lotus feet that produced the waters of the Ganges!</l>
<l>O You who hold a discus, a conch, a staff, a bow, and a sword in [Your] palms!</l>
<l>O God of gods who became a lion! O You on whose chest abides</l>
<l>the Lady on the soft lotus that diffuses honey! O Dark [Lord] with an ocean[-like] body!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
